| `Input.module.scss` | 55 | `rgba($accentPurple, 0.1)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 10%, transparent 90%)` |
| `Input.module.scss` | 63 | `rgba($danger, 0.1)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-danger) 10%, transparent 90%)` |
| `Register.module.scss` | 80 | `rgba($accentPurple, 0.15)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 15%, transparent 85%)` |
| `Landing.module.scss` | 31 | `rgba($accentPurple, 0.15)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 15%, transparent 85%)` |
| `Landing.module.scss` | 32 | `rgba($accentPurple, 0.3)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 30%, transparent 70%)` |
| `Landing.module.scss` | 101 | `rgba($accentPurple, 0.12)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 12%, transparent 88%)` |
| `Landing.module.scss` | 136 | `rgba($accentPurple, 0.15)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 15%, transparent 85%)` |
| `Button.module.scss` | 72 | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)` | `var(--glass-bg)` (approximate, or keep as-is since white overlay is theme-invariant on dark themes) |

